'''默諾威'''（{{lang-en|Monowi}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|m|ɒ|n|oʊ-|w|aɪ}}，或譯'''莫諾維'''）是一座位於[[美國中西部|美國中西部]][[內布拉斯加州|內布拉斯加州]][[博伊德縣_(內布拉斯加州)|博伊德-{zh-cn:县;zh-tw:郡;zh-hk:縣}-]]的建制村落。根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，人口1人，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/DEC/10_PL/P1/1600000US3132550| author=US Census Bureau |title=American FactFinder|accessdate=2011-04-13}}</ref>是美國唯一一座只有一人的建制三級行政區。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/news/pictures/slideshow?articleId=USRTR2LZG0#a=1|title=Monowi, Nebraska, Population: 1|work=[[路透社|路透社]]|date=2011-05-04|accessdate=2017-02-01}}</ref>

「默諾威」在[[美洲原住民|美洲原住民]]語中有「花」的意思，但是該語言尚未被確定。<ref>{{cite book |last=Bright |first=William |title=Native American Placenames of the United States |url=https://archive.org/details/nativeamericanpl0000brig |year=2004 |publisher=University of Oklahoma Press |location=Norman, OK |page=[https://archive.org/details/nativeamericanpl0000brig/page/296 296]}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Chicago and North Western Railway Company|title=A History of the Origin of the Place Names Connected with the Chicago & North Western and Chicago, St. Paul, Minneapolis & Omaha Railways|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OspBAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA104|year=1908|page=104}}</ref>命名為默諾威的原因是因為有許多的野花在村落中生長。<ref>{{cite book | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Dlas_EPVGFEC&source=gbs_navlinks_s | title=Nebraska Place-Names | publisher=University of Nebraska Press | author=Fitzpatrick, Lillian L. | year=1960 | pages=22 | access-date=2017-02-02 | archive-date=2016-11-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116235917/https://books.google.com/books?id=Dlas_EPVGFEC&source=gbs_navlinks_s | dead-url=no }}</ref>

